text: "I was standing in the way of his truck door (and) he kicked me in the stomach to get me out of the way," wrote the woman, who described herself as his former best friend and a previous sexual partner.
title: ‘13 Reasons Why’ actor Uriah Shelton hit with restraining order after allegedly injuring pal with a kick to the stomach
